Ironhide frowned at how this had degenerated. But he knew everyone in
the council would be happy to see the Dinobots leave. He looked down at
Pacifix, "I also want to send an old friend of mine" he said. "Take the
Technobots as well, they have always wanted to go and explore other
planets, and their technology will be of great help" he said looking
down at Pacifix.
